### Create a course
POST {{plamogus-host}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "DSA",
  "title": "Data Structures and Algorithms",
  "description": "Assignments can be completed in any language of choice.",
  "semester": 3
}

### Read all courses
GET {{plamogus-host}}/courses
Accept: application/json

### Read one course
GET {{plamogus-host}}/courses/{id}
Accept: application/json

### Update a course
PUT {{plamogus-host}}/courses/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "DSA",
  "title": "Data Structures and Algorithms",
  "description": "Assignments can be completed in any language of choice.",
  "semester": 3
}

### Delete a course
DELETE {{plamogus-host}}/courses/{id}
